{"tid":756354,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"連登仔成日話反中反共 但日日用緊中資服務","createTime":"2018-07-26T03:37:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-02T08:14:09.000Z","uid":36134,"like":361,"dislike":82,"uniUserReply":70,"replies":[{"pid":"c3e1ab6ba9643314c7cc8f4dfcf92e64448f1ec1","tid":756354,"uid":36134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T03:37:10.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">口裏說不,身體卻很誠實</span></span><br />\n你話避免唔到 我都算<br />\n但明明有好大既選擇空間 但都要奶中奶共<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n手機牌子用華為 小米<br />\n上網用中移動 <br />\n銀行用中銀 中建 招商 工商等中資銀行<br />\n電子支付用支付寶<br />\nMessage用wechat<br />\n旅遊用中旅行<br />\n仲要係中資公司返工 幫助佢地對付港資企業同鯨吞香港市場<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有幾多人一項都唔中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n一項都無既正評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n中左一項或以上既負評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f05ecbd002c77ac50449e02d97324924707d7c33","tid":756354,"uid":36134,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T03:44:47.000Z","msg":"負皮個D人敢唔敢膽現身說法<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0069bca2528a0e4f0a6b02697775e147750544d2","tid":756354,"uid":38194,"like":53,"dislike":0,"score":53,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T03:49:49.000Z","msg":"你講嗰啲我真係一樣都冇中"},{"pid":"7e1b056eee709944e4391eb2e81877f0132b700b","tid":756354,"uid":84212,"like":3,"dislike":82,"score":-79,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T03:52:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a50aca68369f1ee4b31a98e282712bd434656d7d","tid":756354,"uid":84212,"like":4,"dislike":28,"score":-24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T03:53:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"24a5c7c422876fa07275b829b86bed27e8054dd4","tid":756354,"uid":34010,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T04:03:45.000Z","msg":"全部唔中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38a91c07709fb7209eca222cbfe6e3832f40a